data.description: Charming 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhome on a desirable corner lot! This well-maintained residence features an open floor plan, with a modern kitchen-living room combo. Enjoy the convenience of a balcony, and revel in the recently painted interiors. Upgraded kitchen, 2 full baths, and a half bath add to the appeal. Community amenities include a dog park, playground, resort style pool and fitness center. Ideal for those seeking comfort and style in a prime location.
